FBIS3-19736 "drweu055_p_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-055 Document Type:Daily Report 21 Mar 1994 GREECE Government Condemns `Assassination' of Yeoryiadhis NC2103222794 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 2200 GMT 21 Mar 94 NC2103222794 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Government spokesman Evangelos Venizelos today said that the Greek Government expresses its grief and abhorrence at the abominable assassination of Theofilos Yeoryiadhis. The spokesman also expressed the hope that the Cypriot authorities will investigate the case so that the truth may be revealed, not only to the Greeks and Cypriots, but also to the international public.
